541
00:30:22.791 --> 00:30:25.041
<b>Farsz do kwiatów 
cukini.</b>

542
00:30:25.500 --> 00:30:26.291
<b>Ricotta.</b>

543
00:30:28.083 --> 00:30:30.708
<b>Gattino, lubisz ricottę?</b>

544
00:30:31.750 --> 00:30:33.375
<b>Tak chyba tak.</b>

545
00:30:34.083 --> 00:30:34.750
<b>No wreszcie.</b>

546
00:30:35.083 --> 00:30:39.291
<b>Wreszcie 
